review.comments: Kokki's studio was an amazing place to stay in Amsterdam. The location is amazing, 5-15 min walk to all the main attractions and right in the heart of the city. The studio was clean, comfortable and welcoming and it really felt like home for a week. Kokki was helpful and answered quickly to every question. The studio is like you see in the pictures, small but comfortable and well decorated. If you are traveling alone it's the perfect place.
